data.description: LOCATION LOCATION, PRICE REDUCTION - WONT LAST! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with SPACIOUS ROOMS is in a GREAT QUIET Neighborhood in the Heart of EVERYTHING downtown Cape Coral has to offer!! HUGE fenced in YARD w/ shed + PLENTY of ROOM to create your Backyard PARADISE!! PLUS ALL the High ticket updates are done Hurricane Impact windows + Beautiful updated Large kitchen just 5 yrs new w/granite counters, beautiful contemporary cabinets, tile backsplash, stainless appliances + updated bathrooms! Tile throughout, Large entry foyer w/ Beautiful decorative lead glass doors to greet guests. Large liv. room din. room combo adjacent to an open floor plan kitchen great for entertaining + family to gather w/ sliders to a HUGE 25 FT covered indoor/outdoor screened Lanai to enjoy your peaceful yard! This home features a popular split floor plan for privacy with your master bedroom/master bath on one side with sliders to Lanai + guest bedrooms/guest bath on the opposite side. The HUGE family room w/ sliders is adjacent to the guest side of the home. Shopping, Restaurants, Night life, Parks, golf, Yacht Club Boat House restaurant + Cape Coral Beach nearby! Assessments paid - NO damage from Ian!
